---
title: Item Lifecycle
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Private: add(owner, item, details)

    Private --> Private: update details
    Private --> Shared: tag with recipient
    Private --> [*]: remove

    Shared --> Shared: add more tags
    Shared --> Shared: update details
    Shared --> Private: remove all tags
    Shared --> Claimed: recipient claims
    Shared --> [*]: remove

    Claimed --> Claimed: update details
    Claimed --> Shared: claimer unclaims
    Claimed --> Shared: claimer loses access
    Claimed --> [*]: remove

    note right of Private
        Only owner can see
        Not available for claiming
    end note

    note right of Shared
        Owner + tagged recipients can see
        Available for claiming
    end note

    note right of Claimed
        Owner sees as normal item
        Recipients see claim + claimer
        Locked - no one else can claim
    end note
